{"tid":878832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"奧巴馬不點名批評特朗普　指對方及共和黨只會破壞事情","createTime":"2018-10-27T12:27:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T07:57:53.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":111,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"e0d060afb64904b695741ff12f807da4dc18b3b0","tid":878832,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T12:27:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1425184_1_L_20181027201853.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1425184_1_L_20181027201853.jpg&h=97e4ad42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國前總統奧巴馬，不點名批評現任總統特朗普，形容對方及共和黨只會破壞事情。<br />\n<br />\n奧巴馬到密歇根州及威斯康星州，為民主黨參選人在一個多星期之後舉行的中期選舉拉票。他在選舉活動上說，美國人在過去的生活中，沒有見過政客會公然、反覆、赤裸裸及無恥地撒謊。<br />\n<br />\n奧巴馬又提到數以千計正在經墨西哥，湧往美國的民眾，批評共和黨正嘗試說服所有人，害怕這批貧窮及營養不良的難民。奧巴馬說，今次中期選舉，是特朗普執政後首場重要選舉，關乎國家的聲望，他希望國家可以擺脫謊言，走出黑暗的政治環境。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1425184-20181027.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1425184-20181027.htm&d=BBMsXovDUggW2io7Z2ScBTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=861efeee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1425184-20181027.htm&h=d6d6ed59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1425184-20181027.htm</a>"},{"pid":"bfd555a70ffcac42179958f14d9f5e95cb01acdb","tid":878832,"uid":30743,"like":88,"dislike":2,"score":86,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T12:31:07.000Z","msg":"收皮啦，死黑鬼"},{"pid":"46d4803da82d6dc6c967d02f168a0cf336e4a46b","tid":878832,"uid":26329,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T12:34:46.000Z","msg":"屌你老母養cancer<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完全無為世界做野都算，仲要養大毒瘤"},{"pid":"6521a81030a462ca3d1f0c90d8e4751ea5428fc1","tid":878832,"uid":35014,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T12:37:52.000Z","msg